{% comment %}
    ZAE: off-white page background (#FDFCFB) on every page EXCEPT the homepage.
    Homepage keeps its white background. Full-bleed hero / banner sections set
    their own background so they are unaffected. Change the hex here if the
    shade ever needs adjusting.
{% endcomment %}
<style>
    body:not(.template-index) {
        background-color: #FDFCFB;
    }
    body:not(.template-index) .content-for-layout,
    body:not(.template-index) #MainContent {
        background-color: #FDFCFB;
    }
</style>